Package: hydat
Type: Package
Title: Quickly and Efficiently Analyze Datasets from HYDAT
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("David", "Tavernini", email = "taverninid@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
url: https://github.com/dtavern/hydat
bugreports: https://github.com/dtavern/hydat/issues
Description: A few functions in this package allow for a quick manipulation of
    hydat data into "long" format. Additional functions allow for quick calculation
    of mean monthly discharge, generation of hydrographs and rating curves, and to
    also calculate rating curve equations.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.1)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: TRUE
Imports:
    ggplot2,
    magrittr,
    dplyr,
    tidyr
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Suggests: testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
